    "CA 文件会写入 `http.sslCAInfo`。关闭 SSL 验证只适合临时排障；企业网络应优先导入可信 CA 证书。" : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "The CA file is written to `http.sslCAInfo`. Disabling SSL verification is only suitable for temporary troubleshooting; enterprise networks should prioritize importing trusted CA certificates."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "CA 文件会写入 `http.sslCAInfo`。关闭 SSL 验证只适合临时排障；企业网络应优先导入可信 CA 证书。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "CA 檔案會寫入 `http.sslCAInfo`。關閉 SSL 驗證只適合臨時排障；企業網路應優先匯入可信 CA 憑證。"
          }
        },
        "zh-HK" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "CA 檔案會寫入 `http.sslCAInfo`。關閉 SSL 驗證只適合臨時排障；企業網路應優先匯入可信 CA 憑證。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
